snippet.title: 3D Ultra Lionel Traintown Deluxe Intro
snippet.description:
The famed intro, cleverly lifted from my own CD, of the venerable 9-year old train game that many of us grew up with - Re-uploaded with the exact .avi file the game uses upon startup, so turn your volume up and take in that crisp sound, my friends.


Lionel Traintown Deluxe can be found and purchased online, so if you're feeling a bit of nostalgia and don't have your old disk anymore, never fear, because you can get it again.



Damn the music is catchy...
